root: ^Hey there, wolf! Back to see how you're doing.
^If it isn't my helpful fox friend! What brings you back?
^Just wanted to check in and make sure you found that bone alright.
^Oh, I did indeed! Thanks to you, I had a delicious meal.
^Happy to help. And how's everything else going?
^Actually, I've been up to something new.
^Found a very festive tree the other day. You should try looking for it!
^Festive? I will keep that in mind. Take care, wolf friend.
^Thanks for stopping by, fox. And thanks again for helping me out.
